room_title: Escape room "The Lighthouse" by Golden Puzzle Room in Denver
room_description: You are stranded on an island with an abandoned lighthouse. Your boat is in ruins and your supplies are low. Is that a ship on the horizon? If only you could send a signal. But wait, what if you can get the lighthouse to shine again?  Better hurry - that ship will be out of range soon.  Can you fix it in time?
